title: Mountain Men Anonymous
description:
From Lastfm.com:

Mountain Men Anonymous WAS a post-rock band from Gloucestershire via South Glamorgan, Wales. Two members John and Sam have now re-formed as Zail,


Discography includes 2000\&#039;s self-titled demo, 2001\&#039;s self-titled debut, a 7\" split single between the band and Teflon Monkey and their most recent: Krkonose, as well as miscellaneous tracks on various complilations.

According to the band\&#039;s website, they are currently on \"indefinite hiatus.\"
